_aChangeLog.text: Fixed bug with modelindex changing from f7a to f7b.
Fixed a bug where only CT could use the teleporter in Boss Fight lmao

_sText:
jb_resi, a Jailbreak map for CS:Source themed around the Resident Evil franchise.
there are many secrets... many many many more than you will ever find :}

Games:


  • Drop Down / 4 Corners [50/50]
  • Surf
  • Boss Fight
  • Low Grav Bhop / Low Grav Climb [50/50]
  • Colours (s1, s2 & s3)
  • Deathrun (9 traps)
  • Trail Blazing (s1 & s2)
  • Death Crate
  • Extreme Climb
  • HNS
  • Trikz (1 - 7 custom kz tricks)
  • Hunger Games (TP from box in cell area near surf)
  • Dodge Course (s1 & s2)
  • Ladder KZ (easy / hard [50/50])
  • Box Climb (easy/ hard [50/50])
  • Man Cannon
  • Random Climb (1-5 random climbs spawn over the pond)
  • Bomb Toss
  • LJ Blocks
  • Lava Climb (1-3 random climbs over lava (near dodgecourse))
